    public static class DefaultConfigTypeAdapters.NullablePrimitiveTypeAdapter<T>
extends DefaultConfigTypeAdapters.PrimitiveTypeAdapter<T>
    Extension of primitive type adapter that can handle missing config values for primitive types. It replaces missing values with either:
    1. Default values found in the annotation
    2. Java default value for primitive types
    Author:
    Alexander Hoermandinger
